title: dSTORM Imaging and Analysis of Recombination Foci in Mouse Spread Meiotic Nuclei
description: Test data belonging to a protocol paper describing dSTORM imaging and analysis of synaptonemal complex component SYCP3 and RAD51 and DMC1 in mouse spread meiotic nuclei including sample preparation, data acquisition, pre-processing, and data analysis. This data is part of the study described in PLOS Genetics (Koornneef et al. 2022, Multi-color dSTORM microscopy in Hormad1-/- spermatocytes reveals alterations in meiotic recombination intermediates and synaptonemal complex structure).
